text: No, COVID-19 Vaccines Don’t Make You Infertile
The Covid-19 vaccines can render you infertile.
The Covid vaccine will make you infertile.
COVID-19 vaccines threaten people's fertility, no matter their type of reproductive systems.
If you got the Covid-19 vaccine you probably won’t be able to get pregnant.
You might not be able to have children if you have the Covid-19 vaccine.
